description._content: Description: On the road around the "Golden Stairs" en routs to Gach Qaraguli.~ Location: Gach Qaraguli, Persia Description: The encampment on the tableland at Gach Qaraguli where tests were about to begin-1925. Location: Gach Qaraguli, Persia Date: 1925 Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/714 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives.
